            'nav.why': 'Our offer',
            'nav.contact': 'Contact',
            'hero.title1': 'Manufacturer of office,',
            'hero.title2': 'social containers & commercial pavilions',
            'hero.sub': 'We design and manufacture modern modular containers used across many industries. Our range includes office containers, social containers, commercial pavilions, residential containers, and construction site facilities. We deliver both standard builds and custom projects tailored to the investor\'s needs.',
            'hero.cta': 'Contact us',
            'hero.card1.title': 'Industry experience',
            'hero.card1.sub': 'For many years we have been manufacturing containers and modular pavilions for businesses and private clients.',
            'hero.card2.title': 'Custom projects',
            'hero.card2.sub': 'Every container can be designed to the client\'s needs — dimensions, room layout, and equipment.',
            'hero.card3.title': 'Solid construction',
            'hero.card3.sub': 'Our containers are built from durable materials and proven technologies, ensuring long-lasting use.',
            'hero.card4.title': 'Fast delivery',
            'hero.card4.sub': 'Prefabricated modular construction significantly shortens project delivery times.',
            'about.carbon': 'Carbon footprint',
            'about.title': 'Modular container manufacturer',
            'about.p1': '<strong>PROMIR-BUD</strong> is a manufacturer of containers and modular pavilions designed for office, commercial, service, and residential applications. Our projects include office containers, social containers, commercial pavilions, catering containers, and construction site facilities.',
            'about.p2': 'Thanks to modular construction, the units can be easily transported, combined into larger configurations, and adapted to the individual needs of the investor.',
            'about.partners': 'Our partners: Uponor, Würth, Milwaukee, Tarkett, Fibo, Schneider Electric.',
            'about.link': 'See our projects',
            'about.missionHeading': 'Our mission',
            'about.mission': 'Our goal is to deliver affordable homes and commercial spaces quickly and efficiently to everyone who needs them. We are committed to sustainable development and care for the environment. Our buildings comply with the latest industry standards, ensuring quality and safety. We use materials with certifications that confirm their ability to generate a negative carbon footprint and work with trusted suppliers to maintain the highest quality.',
            'about.mission2': 'Quality, experience, and trust — for over 30 years we have been delivering projects that meet the expectations of the most demanding clients. We believe our offer will inspire you to create a space that fits your needs perfectly.',
            'about.partnersLabel': 'Our partners:',
            'services.heading': 'Services we offer',
            'services.design.title': 'Design and project adaptation',
            'services.design.desc': 'Documentation for notification or building permit, filing applications with the authorities. Our design team can assist you through the entire process.',
            'services.foundations.title': 'Foundations and utility connections',
            'services.foundations.desc': 'All work required before module installation can be carried out by our specialised teams.',
            'services.modules.title': 'Module construction',
            'services.modules.desc': 'Family homes in frame technology, holiday units in sandwich panel, or service pavilions. We build everything with the utmost attention to detail and the highest quality.',
            'services.transport.title': 'Transport and assembly',
            'services.transport.desc': 'We won’t leave you on your own here either. We deliver our modules across Europe and carry out installation and commissioning. Our expert team ensures a smooth process from start to finish.',
            'services.turnkey.title': 'Turnkey finishing',
            'services.turnkey.desc': 'We can deliver our modules ready to move in — it all depends on your needs. Finishes can be carried out to our standard specifications or to your custom order.',
            'paulina.badge': 'Frame modules',
            'paulina.title': '“Paulina” – Overview',
            'paulina.p1': 'The “Paulina” modular home is a modern single-storey single-family house that combines functionality with aesthetics. Its facade is finished with silicone structural renders and composite panels, giving it an elegant look and excellent protection against the elements.',
            'paulina.p2': '"Paulina" is available in three floor-area variants, so you can tailor the layout to your needs and preferences. Whether you’re a small family or a larger household, there is a layout to suit you. The interior is designed for comfort and functionality, with spacious rooms and thoughtful layouts for everyday living.',
            'paulina.p3': 'The house also features energy-efficient solutions that help reduce running costs. Modern technology and high-quality building materials make “Paulina” an ideal choice for anyone looking for a comfortable, eco-friendly place to live — a perfect blend of modern design and a cosy home atmosphere.',
            'finishes.title': 'Standard turnkey finishes',
            'finishes.stairs.title': 'Stairs',
            'finishes.stairs.desc': 'Stairs are powder-coated in an elegant black on a single steel profile, with steps in natural oak that complete the interior. Their clean form and carefully chosen materials give the space a modern, stylish look and a warm, welcoming feel. Subtle step lighting adds elegance and character.',
            'finishes.extDoors.title': 'External doors',
            'finishes.extDoors.desc': 'Anthracite-colour security doors, combined with triple-glazed PVC joinery in the same colour on Aluplast Ideal 5000 profile, create a timeless facade. Modern materials ensure excellent thermal and acoustic insulation.',
            'finishes.intDoors.title': 'Internal doors',
            'finishes.intDoors.desc': 'Canis Solid by Windoor, 80 cm wide, is an elegant, solid option. Black handles contrast with the white door surface for a contemporary look.',
            'finishes.floors.title': 'Floors',
            'finishes.floors.desc': 'Standard floors are finished with wood-effect Aqua.Step SPC Southampton panels, which are hard-wearing and easy to maintain. They are moisture-resistant, making them ideal for kitchens and bathrooms.',
            'finishes.kitchens.title': 'Kitchens',
